            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-8 transition-transform duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="text-accent">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="m-0 font-mono text-xl font-bold text-accent">Web Design & Development</h3>
                <p class="flex-grow text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-text-light">Crafting responsive, high-performance websites from scratch. I focus on clean code and user-centric design to build digital experiences that work beautifully on any device.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-8 transition-transform duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="text-accent">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"></line></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="m-0 font-mono text-xl font-bold text-accent">Interactive Prototyping</h3>
                <p class="flex-grow text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-text-light">Bringing ideas to life with high-fidelity, clickable prototypes. This crucial step allows for user testing and validation before a single line of code is written.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-8 transition-transform duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="text-accent">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.73 18a2.64 2.64 0 0 0-3.72 0L12 24l-6.01-6.01a2.64 2.64 0 0 0-3.72 0L0 20.27l6.01-6.01a2.64 2.64 0 0 0 0-3.72L0 4.52l2.27-2.27a2.64 2.64 0 0 0 3.72 0L12 0l6.01 6.01a2.64 2.64 0 0 0 3.72 0L24 8.28l-6.01 6.01a2.64 2.64 0 0 0 0 3.72l6.01 6.01z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="m-0 font-mono text-xl font-bold text-accent">Digital Strategy & Consultation</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">Leveraging user research and analytics to help you make informed decisions. I provide insights that align your digital presence with your business goals for measurable success.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <a href="/services/index" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-heading bg-heading py-3 px-8 font-mono font-bold text-text no-underline transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-[#D36C52] hover:bg-[#D36C52] hover:text-text">View All Services</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="projects-overview">
        <h2 class="m-0 mt-14 mb-6 border-b border-border pb-2 font-mono font-medium text-heading text-xl before:mr-2 before:font-normal before:text-text-light before:content-['##'] md:text-2xl">Creations Overview</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr))] gap-6">
            <div class="group flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface transition-transform duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="aspect-video overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d14bab8c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Abstract code on a screen" class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:scale-105">
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col p-6">
                    <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 font-mono text-xl font-bold text-accent">Echo - Personal Portfolio</h3>
                    <p class="mb-6 flex-grow text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-text-light">The very website you are on. A fully responsive personal hub built with Astro, showcasing a blend of design and modern web technologies.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-[rgba(224,122,95,0.15)] py-1 px-3 text-xs font-medium text-[#B35F48]">Astro</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-[rgba(38,139,210,0.15)] py-1 px-3 text-xs font-medium text-[#268BD2]">CSS</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-[rgba(181,137,0,0.2)] py-1 px-3 text-xs font-medium text-[#b58900]">JavaScript</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
             <div class="group flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface transition-transform duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="aspect-video overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Analytics dashboard with charts and graphs" class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:scale-105">
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col p-6">
                    <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 font-mono text-xl font-bold text-accent">QuantumLeap - SaaS Dashboard</h3>
                    <p class="mb-4">A UI/UX concept for a next-generation analytics platform, focusing on data visualization and intuitive user workflows.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-[rgba(163,55,240,0.1)] py-1 px-3 text-xs font-medium text-[#8327c3]">Figma</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-tag-bg py-1 px-3 text-xs font-medium text-accent">UI/UX</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-[rgba(188,71,73,0.15)] py-1 px-3 text-xs font-medium text-[#BC4749]">Prototyping</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
             <div class="group flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface transition-transform duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="aspect-video overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587620962725-abab7fe55159?q=80&w=1931&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Laptop with code and abstract shapes" class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:scale-105">
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-grow flex-col p-6">
                    <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 font-mono text-xl font-bold text-accent">CodeGenius - AI Assistant UI</h3>
                    <p class="mb-4">An interface design for an AI-powered code completion tool, designed to be unobtrusive yet powerful for developers.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-[rgba(42,161,152,0.15)] py-1 px-3 text-xs font-medium text-[#2AA198]">UI Design</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-[rgba(203,75,22,0.15)] py-1 px-3 text-xs font-medium text-[#CB4B16]">UX Research</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <a href="/projects/index" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-heading bg-heading py-3 px-8 font-mono font-bold text-text no-underline transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-[#D36C52] hover:bg-[#D36C52] hover:text-text">View All Projects</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="forms-section">
        <h2 class="m-0 mt-14 mb-6 border-b border-border pb-2 font-mono font-medium text-heading text-xl before:mr-2 before:font-normal before:text-text-light before:content-['##'] md:text-2xl">Connect</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-8">
                <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 font-mono text-xl font-bold text-accent">Contact Me</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">Have a question or a project in mind? Let's talk. I'm always open to discussing new ideas and opportunities.</p>
                <form action="#" method="POST">
                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <label for="name" class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-text">Name</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="box-border w-full rounded-md border border-border bg-surface p-3 font-mono text-base text-text focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/50">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <label for="email" class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-text">Email</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="box-border w-full rounded-md border border-border bg-surface p-3 font-mono text-base text-text focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/50">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <label for="message" class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-text">Message</label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required class="box-border w-full min-h-[120px] resize-y rounded-md border border-border bg-surface p-3 font-mono text-base text-text focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/50"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-heading bg-heading py-3 px-8 font-mono font-bold text-text no-underline transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-[#D36C52] hover:bg-[#D36C52] hover:text-text">Send Message</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-8">
